@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Carbon Tracking - Carbon Tracker</PageTitle>

<div class="about-container">
    <section class="about-hero parallax-section">
        <div class="about-hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text-content">
                <h1 class="glow-text">Understanding Carbon Tracking</h1>
                <p class="lead shimmer-text">Your Gateway to Environmental Consciousness</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-visual">
                <div class="earth-animation">
                    <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="orbit-circle"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-story">
        <div class="story-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="gradient-text">Why Carbon Tracking Matters</h2>
                <div class="underline"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <p class="enhanced-text">Carbon tracking is more than just numbers â€“ it's about understanding our impact on the planet and taking meaningful action. Every day, our activities contribute to greenhouse gas emissions, from driving cars to using electricity and consuming products.</p>
                
                <div class="fact-box glass-effect">
                    <div class="fact-icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle pulse"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p>Did you know? The average person's carbon footprint is about 4 tons per year, while the global target to combat climate change is 2 tons per person.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="gradient-text">The Climate Crisis</h2>
                <div class="underline"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="enhanced-text section-intro">Our planet faces unprecedented challenges due to climate change:</p>
            <div class="impact-grid">
                <div class="impact-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-temperature-high"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Rising Temperatures</h3>
                        <p>Global temperatures continue to rise at an alarming rate</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-water"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Rising Seas</h3>
                        <p>Coastal communities threatened by rising sea levels</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-wind"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Extreme Weather</h3>
                        <p>Increased frequency of natural disasters</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-tree"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Biodiversity Loss</h3>
                        <p>Ecosystems and species facing extinction</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="gradient-text">How Carbon Tracking Helps</h2>
                <div class="underline"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Awareness</h3>
                    <p>Understanding your carbon footprint is the first step toward reducing it</p>
                    <div class="card-decoration"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Informed Decisions</h3>
                    <p>Make better choices based on real environmental impact data</p>
                    <div class="card-decoration"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Personal Impact</h3>
                    <p>See how your individual actions contribute to global change</p>
                    <div class="card-decoration"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-card glass-effect">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Collective Action</h3>
                    <p>Join a community committed to environmental sustainability</p>
                    <div class="card-decoration"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-section fade-in">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="gradient-text">Take Action Today</h2>
                <div class="underline"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-content">
                <p class="enhanced-text">Every journey begins with a single step. Start tracking your carbon footprint today and join millions of others in the fight against climate change.</p>
                <div class="action-buttons">
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-glow">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                        Start Your Journey
                    </a>
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline btn-glass">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                        Back to Home
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
